ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v231.message

Class RCL_I06

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractStructure
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractGroup
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractMessage
          • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v231.message.RCL_I06
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Group, Message, Structure, Visitable, Serializable

    public class RCL_I06
extends AbstractMessage

    Represents a RCL_I06 message structure (see chapter ?). This structure contains the following elements:

    • 1: MSH (MSH - message header segment)
    • 2: MSA (MSA - message acknowledgment segment)
    • 3: QRD (QRD - original-style query definition segment)
    • 4: QRF (QRF - original style query filter segment) optional
    • 5: RCL_I06_PRDCTD (a Group object) repeating
    • 6: PID (PID - patient identification segment)
    • 7: DG1 (DG1 - diagnosis segment) optional repeating
    • 8: DRG (DRG - diagnosis related group segment) optional repeating
    • 9: AL1 (AL1 - patient allergy information segment) optional repeating
    • 10: NTE (NTE - notes and comments segment) optional repeating
    • 11: DSP (DSP - display data segment) optional repeating
    • 12: DSC (DSC - Continuation pointer segment) optional
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
